  "_meta": {
    "comment": "Species XP weight. Multiplicative on top of tier_weight x mlvl_scale in Nat20XpOnKillSystem. Missing entries default to 1.0.",
    "baseline": "Trork_Warrior (HP 61, damage 23, product 1403)",
    "formula": "weight = clamp(0.1, 8.0, round1((HP * damage) / 1403))",
    "tier_interaction": "Applied multiplicatively AFTER killXpWeight(tier) * normalMobXpMult(if diffTier==null). Nat20-affixed CHAMPION/BOSS already outscale native same-species via the tier weight (CHAMPION 2.5 vs REGULAR 1.0*0.5=0.5, so 5x); species multiplier is orthogonal and preserves intra-tier ordering.",
